\pard\tx283\pardeftab720\li600\fi-300\sl360\slmult1\sb50\sa120
\cf0 \'95	Strengthens the market for locally-sourced energy products, particularly when biomass is produced from waste and residual woods which are byproducts of forestry and manufacturing within the region. This supports the local clean energy economy and job growth (Massachusetts Department of Energy Resources, 2015). \
